{"article_id":"Eu61V8twAJT12zD9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sen. Ted Cruz was projected to win the Wisconsin primary Tuesday ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"delivering a stunning blow to GOP presidential front-runner Donald Trump","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"and resetting the race","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as it heads east later this month .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Networks called the race","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"soon after polls closed at 9 p.m. eastern time ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"based on exit polling","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that showed Mr. Cruz with a sizable lead .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"With 37 percent of the precincts reporting ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Cruz led Mr. Trump by 53 percent to 30 percent ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"followed by Mr. Kasich with 15 percent .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" Tonight is a turning point .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Tonight is a rallying cry , \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Cruz said at his election night party .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" It is a call from the hardworking men and women of Wisconsin to the people of America :","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"We have a choice , a real choice . \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Mr. Cruz said","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the victory is a sign of his growing momentum ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and highlighted the backing","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"he has received from five of his former GOP presidential rivals ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"as well as the recent contests in Utah , Colorado and North Dakota","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"has convinced him","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"he is going to earn the 1,237 delegates","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"needed","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to win the nomination before the Republican National Convention .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"\" Either before Cleveland or at the convention in Cleveland , together we will the majority of the delegates","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and together we will beat Hillary Clinton in November , \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Cruz said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Cruz had said","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"a victory would show","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he is consolidating the anti-Trump voters within the GOP behind his bid ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and indeed that appeared to be the case","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"as he and Mr. Trump went head-to-head ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"making multiple appearances a day","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to try to build support .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"\" We are winning","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"because we are uniting the Republican party , \"","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Mr. Cruz said .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"But Mr. Trump was unable to recover from a bad week","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that saw his campaign manager charged with simple battery after an altercation with a reporter ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"and saw the candidate himself stumble on abortion and other points of conservative orthodoxy .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"He also faced a barrage of questions about his sliding poll numbers among female voters ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"leading him to deploy his wife Melania on the campaign trail .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"The Cruz victory also makes it tougher for Mr. Trump to win the nomination outright on a first ballot at the July convention .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"Ohio Gov . John Kasich , the third man in the race , insisted","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"he ' s staying in","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"despite another loss .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"\" The nomination contest is now wide open ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" Kasich campaign strategist John Weaver said in a memo","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"issued","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"just before polls closed .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"\" This week will be remembered as the one","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"in which Ted Cruz and Donald Trump both effectively admitted","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"they will not reach the GOP Convention with enough bound delegates","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to be the nominee . \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Kasich argues ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and polling confirms ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that he runs the best of the three GOP candidates against Democratic front-runner Hillary Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"But GOP primary voters have paid little attention to that","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"as they pick their champion .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Mr. Trump is hoping to avoid a contested convention ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"which would give most delegates","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"- many of them party regulars","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that are not thrilled with Mr. Trump -","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"the chance","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to cast their support behind whoever they please after the first ballot .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Trump has said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that it would be hard for the GOP to redirect the nomination to another candidate","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"if he entered the convention close to the magic number of delegates","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"needed .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Exit polls out of Wisconsin showed","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that 56 percent of GOP voters said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the candidates","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"that has collected the most votes in the primaries","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"should win the party ' s nomination .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Four in 10 , meanwhile , said","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"they favor a contested convention ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"and that delegates should tap the nominee .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s fingerprints were all over the exit polls ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"with seven in ten voters saying","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"they support his proposal","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"to put a temporary freeze on non-US Muslims","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"entering the country .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Exit polls also showed","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"that trade weighed heavily on the minds of Republican voters ,","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"with over half of them saying","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"the United States was getting the raw end of trade deals .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Six in ten GOP voters said","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"illegal immigrants should be offered a path to citizenship ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"which is higher","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"than what came out of most other primary states ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"and a third called for their deportation .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"Half of the voters sought a candidate with political experience ,","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"and about half said","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"they wanted a candidate from outside the political establishment .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Mr. Cruz , meanwhile , was seen as the GOP ' s best bet","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"to beat Hillary Clinton in a general election match-up ,","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"followed by Mr. Trump and Mr. Kasich .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":199,"left":144,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":103,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":102,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":1,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":138,"right":142,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":128,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":114,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":109,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","n